}}  '''EncroChat'''是一家位于[[欧洲|欧洲]]的被用於非法活動的[[电信网络|電信網絡]]，其包括[[硬體|硬體]]、[[作業系統|作業系統]]、[[軟體|軟體]]、[[資料傳輸|資料傳輸]]與[[伺服器|伺服器]]<ref name=it/>。

EncroChat的用戶端是裝有加密傳訊程式的[[Android|Android]]手機，EncroChat用戶透過EncroChat的伺服器傳送訊息。而用戶的[[Android|Android]]手機系統是EncroChat開發的定製版Android系統EncroChat OS。EncroChat的[[伺服器|伺服器]]位於[[法國|法國]]<ref name=it>{{Cite web|title=歐洲摧毀遭犯罪集團利用的EncroChat加密手機網路|url=https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/138630|accessdate=|author=ithome|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710085943/https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/138630|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年，法國司法機關發現EncroChat手機被一些有組織的罪犯用來當作加密通訊工具。2020年3月至2020年6月，多國警方對其進行深入調查。同年6月12日至13日，在警方的搗毀下EncroChat停止運作<ref name="vicehow">{{Cite news|author=Cox|first=Joseph|date=2 July 2020|title=How Police Secretly Took Over a Global Phone Network for Organised Crime|work=[[Vice_Motherboard|Vice Motherboard]]|url=https://www.vice.com/en_uk/article/3aza95/how-police-secretly-took-over-a-global-phone-network-for-organised-crime|accessdate=2020-07-10|archive-date=2020-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711115917/https://www.vice.com/en_uk/article/3aza95/how-police-secretly-took-over-a-global-phone-network-for-organised-crime|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="FinancialTimes">{{Cite news|author=Wright|first=Robert|date=2 July 2020|title=Hundreds arrested across Europe as French police crack encrypted network|work=[[The_Financial_Times|The Financial Times]]|url=https://www.ft.com/content/7006913f-be3d-49b5-8ba7-7c5b78b551b2|accessdate=2020-07-10|archive-date=2020-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710121833/https://www.ft.com/content/7006913f-be3d-49b5-8ba7-7c5b78b551b2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

EncroChat被关闭时大约有60,000名訂閱用戶。<ref name="BBC7July20">{{Cite news|author=Staff|date=7 July 2020|title=Six arrested after 'Dutch torture chambers' found|work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-53325388|accessdate=2020-07-10|archive-date=2020-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710091956/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-53325388|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Euronews">{{Cite news|author=Kennedy|first=Rachael|date=2 July 2020|title=EU authorities penetrate phone network in huge organised crime sting|work=[[Euronews|Euronews]]|url=https://www.euronews.com/2020/07/02/encrochat-european-authorities-compromise-phone-network-to-arrest-untouchable-criminals-in|accessdate=2020-07-10|archive-date=2020-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200709164112/https://www.euronews.com/2020/07/02/encrochat-european-authorities-compromise-phone-network-to-arrest-untouchable-criminals-in|dead-url=no}}</ref>截至2020年7月7日，全欧洲至少有800人被捕，19個合成毒品實驗室被查獲，9,200公斤的[[毒品|毒品]]、[[武器|武器]]以及2,000萬歐元的[[現金|現金]]被扣押<ref name=it/>。    

